<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
       "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="<%=image_path('cal.ico')%>" />
<title><%= @page_title || "UCB SPH CCLS" -%></title>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home_exposure','scaffold' %>
<%#= stylesheet_link_tag controller.controller_name %>
<%= javascript_include_tag :defaults %>
<%= yield :head %>
</head>
<body>
<div id='container'>
<div id='header'>
<div id='minimenu'>
	<%= link_to "Home", home_exposure_path %>&nbsp;|&nbsp;
	<a>Reports</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;
	<a>FAQs</a>
</div><!-- minimenu -->
<div id='fullsearch'>
<form action='search'>
	<input type='text' />
	<input type='submit' value='Find' />
</form>
</div>
<div id='mainmenu'>
	<%= link_to "Subjects", he_subjects_path, 
		:class => (controller.controller_name == 'subjects')?'current':nil %>
	<%= link_to "Enroll", he_enrolls_path, 
		:class => (controller.controller_name == 'enrolls')?'current':nil %>
	<%= link_to "Interview", he_interviews_path, 
		:class => (controller.controller_name == 'interviews')?'current':nil %>
	<%= link_to "Samples", he_samples_path, 
		:class => (controller.controller_name == 'samples')?'current':nil %>
	<%= link_to "Follow-Up", he_followups_path, 
		:class => (controller.controller_name == 'followups')?'current':nil %>
</div><!-- mainmenu -->
</div><!-- header -->
<div id='columns' class='equal_height_column_wrapper'>
<div id='main' class='equal_height_column'>
<%= yield :main %>
<div id='content_wrapper' class='equal_height_column'>
<div id='content'>
<% flash.each do |key, msg| %>
 <%= content_tag :p, msg, :id => key, :class => 'flash' %>
<% end %>
<noscript>
<p id='noscript' class='flash'>Javascript is required for this site to be fully functional.</p>
</noscript>
<%= yield %>
</div><!-- content -->
<%= yield :content_bottom %>
</div><!-- content_wrapper -->
</div><!-- main -->
<div id='guidance' class='equal_height_column'>
<h3>Guidance</h3>
Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
<%= yield :guidance %>
</div><!-- guidance -->
</div><!-- columns -->
<div id='footer'>
<p>
<small>2010 California Childhood Leukemia Study, UC Berkeley School of Public Health</small>
</p>
</div><!-- footer -->
</div><!-- container -->
</body>
</html>
